       standard input instead.

       If _b_o_x@@_d_o_m_a_i_n is not on the mailing list, eezzmmllmm--uunnssuubb keeps it off.

       eezzmmllmm--uunnssuubb  converts  _d_o_m_a_i_n  to  lowercase before removing _b_o_x@@_d_o_m_a_i_n
